title: BSC mainnet - Initial sync stops
body:
#### System information

Erigon version: 2022.99.99-dev-0e457ba9

OS & Version: Windows 10 Pro, Version 20H2, OS Build: 19042.1706

Commit hash : 0e457ba9

#### Expected behaviour
Sync BSC mainnet


#### Actual behaviour
Sync stops, no errors

#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour
Arguments: erigon.exe --chain bsc --datadir N:/erigon --prune hrtc --rpc.batch.concurrency 50 --torrent.download.rate=60mb --torrent.upload.rate=2mb --maxpeers 50 --ethash.dagdir N:/erigon/erigon-ethash --private.api.addr=localhost:9090 --http --ws --http.addr 192.168.2.6 --http.port 8545 --http.api=eth,debug,net,trace,web3,erigon --syncmode full
